## ReKameo - ignored files

# Visual Studio / IDE droppings
.vs/
.vscode/
ReKameo.code-workspace

# Build output
/out/
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.exp
*.lib
*.exe

# rexglue migrate backups
CMakeLists.txt.bak
src/main.cpp.bak

# Generated recomp sources (regenerated by `rexglue migrate`)
/generated/

# Runtime logs & drop-in files produced by Play*.bat
/logs/
kameo
kameo.exe
kameo.pdb

# Game assets extracted from the user's ISO
# (the ISO itself and anything derived from it must NEVER be committed)
/kameo.iso
/assets/
!/assets/.gitkeep
/out/iso_extract/

# Third-party tools dropped by the user locally.
# Ignore the tree, but keep the scripts and README we wrote.
/tools/*
!/tools/README.md
!/tools/*.ps1
